IAEA Says Iran is Upgrading Nuclear Equipment, WSJ Says

-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 
2011-02-18T16:51:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-18/iaea-says-iran-is-upgrading-nuclear-equipment-wsj-says.html
  Iran  is stepping up its efforts to
enrich uranium by improving the equipment at its nuclear
facilities after its enrichment program was disrupted by a
computer virus, the Wall Street Journal reported on its website,
citing unidentified diplomats familiar with a new assessment by
the  International Atomic Energy Agency .  The IAEA believes Iran wants to replace thousands of
centrifuges it uses for  uranium enrichment  with more modern,
carbon-fiber centrifuges, the Journal reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  